#. Tag: title
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "DESCRIPTION"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kpatience; is a compendium of several well known patience card games, "
"ranging from the well known Klondike and Freecell, to lesser known games "
"such as Grandfather's Clock and Mod3. In all there are 12 variations for you "
"to while away time."
msgstr ""
"&kpatience; est un condensé de plusieurs jeux de patience biens connus, "
"allant des célèbres Klondike et Freecell, aux jeux moins connus comme "
"« Grandfather's Clock » et « Mod3 ». En tout, 12 variations pour que vous "
"puissiez passer du temps."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "OPTIONS"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This program follows the usual GNU command line syntax, with long options "
"starting with two dashes (`--'). A summary of the options supported by "
"<command>kpat</command> is included below."
msgstr ""
"Ce logiciel suit la syntaxe en ligne de commande usuelle GNU, avec les "
"options longues commençant avec deux tirets (« -- »). Un résumé des options "
"prises en charge par <command>kpat</command> est inclus ci-dessous."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option> <option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<option>-h</option> <option>--help</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "This lists the options available at the command line"
msgstr "Ceci affiche la liste des options disponibles en ligne de commandes."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option> <option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>-v</option> <option>--version</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists version information for &kpatience;"
msgstr "Affiche la liste des informations de version de &kpatience;"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--solvegame</option> <replaceable> file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--solvegame</option> <replaceable> fichier</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to find a solution to the given savegame"
msgstr "Essayez de trouver une solution à la partie enregistrée fournie"

